# EMC Design System

## Token Source

All design tokens live in `web-src/src/styles/designSystem.ts`.
Import tokens from there — **do not use magic numbers**.

```tsx
import {
  SPACING, FORM_SPACING, LAYOUT_DIMENSIONS,
  COLORS, TYPOGRAPHY, Z_INDEX, BORDERS,
  STICKY_GNAV_STYLES, FIXED_ACTION_BAR_STYLES,
  SCROLLABLE_CONTENT_STYLES, SIDE_NAV_STICKY_STYLES,
  LAYOUT_PATTERNS, FLEX_GAP,
} from '../../styles/designSystem'
```

## Spacing System (8px grid)

| Token       | Value | Use Case                      |
| ----------- | ----- | ----------------------------- |
| `SPACING.NONE` | 0px | No spacing                   |
| `SPACING.XXS`  | 4px | Label-to-input gap           |
| `SPACING.XS`   | 8px | Tight spacing                |
| `SPACING.SM`   | 12px | Small gaps                  |
| `SPACING.MD`   | 16px | Default field gap            |
| `SPACING.LG`   | 24px | Section gaps, card padding   |
| `SPACING.XL`   | 32px | Large section gaps           |
| `SPACING.XXL`  | 40px | Major separations            |
| `SPACING.XXXL` | 48px | Page-level spacing           |
| `SPACING.HUGE` | 64px | Hero-level spacing           |
| `SPACING.MAX`  | 80px | Maximum spacing              |

### Form-Specific Spacing
```tsx
FORM_SPACING.SECTION_GAP   // 24px — between form cards
FORM_SPACING.FIELD_GAP     // 16px — between fields within a section
FORM_SPACING.LABEL_GAP     // 4px  — between label and input
FORM_SPACING.CARD_PADDING  // 24px — inside form cards
FORM_SPACING.HEADING_GAP   // 12px — heading to content
```

## Layout Dimensions

```tsx
LAYOUT_DIMENSIONS.GNAV_HEIGHT      // 56px  (TopNav)
LAYOUT_DIMENSIONS.ACTION_BAR_HEIGHT // 60px  (FormWizard action bar)
LAYOUT_DIMENSIONS.SIDE_NAV_WIDTH   // 240px (FormWizard step nav)
```

### Calculated Heights
```tsx
SAFE_AREA_HEIGHT           // 121px (gnav + action bar + padding)
FORM_CONTENT_HEIGHT        // calc(100vh - 121px)
CONTENT_HEIGHT_NO_ACTION_BAR // calc(100vh - 56px)
```

## Colors

### Brand Colors
- `COLORS.ADOBE_RED` (`#EB1000`) — Adobe brand red, used in step headings

### Spectrum CSS Variables (preferred for theme consistency)
- `COLORS.GRAY_100` through `COLORS.GRAY_800` — via `var(--spectrum-global-color-gray-*)`
- `COLORS.BLUE_400` — links and accents
- `COLORS.RED_600` — errors and destructive actions

### Status Colors
- `COLORS.STATUS_DRAFT` (`#2D9D92`) — teal
- `COLORS.STATUS_PUBLISHED` (`#CD3ACE`) — purple
- `COLORS.STATUS_ARCHIVED` (`#666666`) — gray
- `COLORS.STATUS_CANCELLED` (`#D7373F`) — red

## Typography Tokens

| Token                          | Size  | Weight | Use Case                    |
| ------------------------------ | ----- | ------ | --------------------------- |
| `TYPOGRAPHY.STEP_HEADING`      | 24px  | 900    | Wizard step titles          |
| `TYPOGRAPHY.COMPONENT_HEADING` | 28px  | 700    | Section headings            |
| `TYPOGRAPHY.SUBSECTION_HEADING`| 18px  | 700    | Subsection headings         |
| `TYPOGRAPHY.FIELD_LABEL`       | 14px  | 600    | Field labels                |
| `TYPOGRAPHY.HELPER_TEXT`       | 12px  | 400    | Helper/description text     |
| `TYPOGRAPHY.SECTION_DESCRIPTION`| 14px | 400    | Section description text    |

**Note:** All typography tokens have `margin: 0`. Use container `gap` for spacing.

